org.cef.callback

Class CefDragData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cef.callback.CefDragData

  • public abstract class CefDragData
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used to represent drag data. The methods of this class may be called on any thread.(用于表示拖动数据的类。这个类的方法可以在任何线程上调用。)

      • getFileContents

        public abstract int getFileContents(java.io.OutputStream writer)
        Write the contents of the file being dragged out of the web view into |writer|. Returns the number of bytes sent to |writer|. If |writer| is NULL this method will return the size of the file contents in bytes. Call getFileName() to get a suggested name for the file.(将从web视图中拖出来的文件的内容写入|writer|。返回发送到|writer|的字节数。如果|writer|为NULL，此方法将返回文件内容的大小（以字节为单位）。调用getFileName()获取文件的建议名称。)
        Parameters:
        writer - Writes the contents into this object.(writer-将内容写入此对象。)
        Returns:
        The number of bytes sent to writer. If writer is NULL the size of the file contents in bytes is returned.(发送到写入程序的字节数。如果写入程序为NULL，则返回以字节为单位的文件内容大小。)
